flex;\">\n          <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: middle;font-size: 16px;padding-left: 10px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n           <p data-brushtype=\"text\"><span style=\"color: #138bde;\"><strong><span leaf=\"\">第二梯队：组合技发挥最大威力</span></strong></span></p>\n          </div>\n         </div>\n        </div>\n        <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 5px;font-family: sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">1）场景：统计每分钟超时错误的数量</span></span></p>\n        <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n        <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n        <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"apache\"><code><span leaf=\"\"><span class=\"code-snippet__attribute\">grep</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">\"Timeout\"</span>&nbsp;application.log |&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">\\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">sed -n 's/.*\\(<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">2023</span>-<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">11</span>-<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">15</span>&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">14</span>:[<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>-<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">9</span>][<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">0</span>-<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">9</span>]\\).*/\\<span class=\"code-snippet__number\">1</span>/p' |&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">\\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">sort |&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__punctuation\">\\</span></span></code><br><code><span leaf=\"\">uniq -c</span></code><br></pre>\n        <p></p>\n        <p style=\"box-sizing: border-box;padding: 0px 5px;font-family: sans-serif;line-height: 1.75em;\"><span leaf=\"\" style=\"font-size:15px;\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-weight: bold;\">2）场景：分析Nginx日志，找出返回码非200的请求IP</span></span></p>\n        <p class=\"code-snippet__fix code-snippet__js\"></p>\n        <ul class=\"code-snippet__line-index code-snippet__js\"></ul>\n        <pre class=\"code-snippet__js\" data-lang=\"bash\"><code><span leaf=\"\">awk&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__string\">'$9 != 200 {print $1}'</span>&nbsp;access.log |&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">sort</span>&nbsp;|&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">uniq</span>&nbsp;-c |&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">sort</span>&nbsp;-nr |&nbsp;<span class=\"code-snippet__built_in\">head</span>&nbsp;-20</span></code></pre>\n        <p></p>\n       </div>\n       <div data-role=\"paragraph\" style=\"font-family:sans-serif;\">\n        <p style=\"padding:0px 0.5em;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: #888888;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">作者丨</span><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: #888888;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\" data-pm-slice=\"1 1 [&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-role&quot;:&quot;outer&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;article135&quot;,&quot;label&quot;:&quot;edit by 135editor&quot;,&quot;data-tplid&quot;:&quot;291729&quot;,&quot;data-pm-slice&quot;:&quot;0 0 []&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;_135editor&quot;,&quot;data-tools&quot;:&quot;135编辑器&quot;,&quot;data-id&quot;:&quot;us-3745001&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;class&quot;:&quot;article135&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;box-sizing: border-box; padding:0 5px;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-role&quot;:&quot;paragraph&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;_135editor&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-role&quot;:&quot;paragraph&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;_135editor&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;data-role&quot;:&quot;paragraph&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;_135editor&quot;,&quot;style&quot;:&quot;font-family:sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;para&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;section&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; color: #333333; background-color: #ffffff; font-size: 16px; line-height: 1.5em; letter-spacing: 0.5px; text-align: left; font-family:sans-serif;&quot;,&quot;class&quot;:&quot;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;},&quot;node&quot;,{&quot;tagName&quot;:&quot;span&quot;,&quot;attributes&quot;:{&quot;style&quot;:&quot;margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: #888888; font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;&quot;},&quot;namespaceURI&quot;:&quot;http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml&quot;}]\">北漂程序员老郑</span></span></span></p>\n        <p style=\"padding:0px 0.5em;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: #888888;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">来源丨公众号：北漂程序员老郑（ID：</span><span leaf=\"\">LaoZheng_NB</span><span leaf=\"\">）</span></span></p>\n        <p style=\"padding:0px 0.5em;margin:0px;max-width:100%;letter-spacing:0.5px;font-size:16px;line-height:1.5em;font-family:sans-serif;box-sizing:border-box !important;overflow-wrap:break-word !important;text-align:justify;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: #888888;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">dbaplus社群欢迎广大技术人员投稿，投稿邮箱：</span></span><span style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;max-width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box !important;overflow-wrap: break-word !important;font-size: 14px;color: #888888;font-family:Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;\"><span leaf=\"\">editor@dbaplus.cn</span></span></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n  <p></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "本文通过实际案例，系统性地介绍了如何利用 grep 及其组合命令高效排查日志，涵盖完整堆栈捕获、实时监控、压缩日志分析及高级统计等多种实用场景。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "本文通过实际案例，系统性地介绍了如何利用 grep 及其组合命令高效排查日志，涵盖完整堆栈捕获、实时监控、压缩日志分析及高级统计等多种实用场景。",
  "summary": "文章以一个新同事低效查日志的场景引入，引出了基于 grep 的一系列高效日志排查方法。首先指出传统 tail -f | grep 和 vi 搜索的局限性，例如丢失堆栈信息、视觉疲劳和处理压缩文件困难等。随后，文章详细介绍了 grep 组合拳的四类实战场景，包括利用 -A 参数捕获完整异常堆栈、实时监控与上下文保留、使用 zgrep 直接分析压缩日志，以及结合管道进行异常趋势统计。文章还进一步分享了 grep 的高级参数应用、多维度日志关联分析、性能敏感场景优化和正则表达式调优技巧。最后，扩展了工具链，介绍了 wc、awk、sed 等常用命令及其组合，展示了在统计错误、字段提取、文本清洗等方面的强大功能，旨在帮助开发者大幅提升日志分析效率。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "传统 `tail -f | grep` 无法捕获完整的异常堆栈信息，导致问题定位困难。",
      "explanation": "这种方式只能匹配单行异常，无法显示异常的上下 N 行上下文，使得开发人员难以获取故障发生的完整背景信息和调用链，增加了排查难度。"
    },
    {
      "point": "利用 `grep -A N` 可有效捕获完整异常堆栈，提高故障排查效率。",
      "explanation": "`grep` 的 `-A` 参数能够显示匹配行后的 N 行，对于日志中的异常堆栈信息捕获至关重要，能帮助开发者快速获取完整的错误上下文，加速问题定位。"
    },
    {
      "point": "`zgrep` 命令允许直接分析压缩日志文件，无需手动解压，显著提升效率。",
      "explanation": "在生产环境中，日志常以压缩格式存储。`zgrep` 内置支持 `.gz` 格式，避免了冗余的解压步骤，保持了工作流的连贯性，节省了宝贵的排查时间。"
    },
    {
      "point": "通过组合 `grep`、`awk`、`sed` 等命令，可实现高级日志分析和统计功能。",
      "explanation": "这些命令的灵活组合，可以实现按时间窗口过滤、字段提取、错误频率统计等复杂任务，将日志数据转化为有价值的洞察，辅助进行系统性能优化和模式发现。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "tail -f | grep 只能捕获异常片段，丢失关键堆栈信息。",
    "zgrep -H -A50 \"OutOfMemoryError\" *.gz  # 跳过解压步骤，直击问题核心",
    "grep -v \"健康检查|心跳\" app.log | grep -A30 \"异常\" # 排除干扰信息，聚焦核心问题",
    "awk '$9 != 200 {print $1}' access.log | sort | uniq -c | sort -nr | head -20 # 分析 Nginx 日志，找出返回码非 200 的请求 IP"
  ],
